Paper: hep-th/9303080

Date: 1993-03-15

Title: Non-Abelian Chern-Simons Quantum Mechanics

Authors: Taejin Lee and Phillial Oh

Comments: 11 pages, SNUTP-93-4

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 72 (1994) 1141-1144

We propose a classical model for the non-Abelian Chern-Simons theory coupledto $N$ point-like sources and quantize the system using the BRST technique. Theresulting quantum mechanics provides a unified framework for fractional spin,braid statistics and Knizhnik-Zamolodchikov equation.